cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper proposes a novel image descriptor for large scale image search, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed descriptor incorporates weak geometry information, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) fields. The paper also presents a technique for learning the membership function, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
